column5: Time for me to get sleeping after a long day at work but hopefully you all have a good day. As for me I'll catch the next morning that comes around
And good mornin to you too Bill, looks like another fine day starting up  I'm heading out shortly to take the pooch for a walk down to Ashbridges Bay and catch the sunrise over Lake O
Good morning Bill, I hope the headache is gone. Time for me to hit the sack too! -Brian

Lol, it is gone thankfully... I hate how if I get on here I get suckered into reading and catching up. Lew, it sure seems like it will end up being a nice enough day, was mild all night, getting closer to worm pickin time
I feel like such bum when you guys are posting at 5:30 AM. But then again, I love my sleep haha (in the winter that is)
Well this is morning #2 for me lol, now I am up for the day!!!
